divs: sighting detailsabout 2:25am 3-21-2009 i was sleeping in my bed and somebody was talking to me and i felt something like a persons elbow aginst my middle of the outside upper left leg as i was ln a fetal position lying on my right side and it was dark in my room. except for the dim light about 50 feet from my window in the apartments. i awaken to see a invisable thin person move a way from me and disaper into the darkness, and i kept saying jahovah over and over i was scaired and i lyed there awake for a few minites and i got up and turned on the light till about 6:00am i sleep some in that time frame then i went back to sleep again after i turn off the light. i have a camera at arms lenth 2 1\2 feet away but the encounter did not last long enuff for me to think of grabing it. it normaly does not as i awaken they leave and they know they can get away. i wish they would let me take at least one or more good picture of them i dont think i will ever get use to this even after all these years, i think its a lack of info from them.
